# ==========================
### IntelliJ IDEA ###
.idea/
*.iws
*.iml
*.ipr

### VS Code ###
.vscode/

### Eclipse / STS ###
.apt_generated
.classpath
.factorypath
.project
.settings
.springBeans
.sts4-cache
bin/

### NetBeans ###
/nbproject/private/
/nbbuild/
/dist/
/nbdist/
/.nb-gradle/
build/

